data.name: RichTextBox_Manual.Text
data.value:
There are six activities about transformer banking connections implanted in this software, namely: wye-wye, wye-delta, delta-delta, delta-wye, open-delta, and open wye-open delta connections.
Before proceeding to the transformer banking trainer, there is a short discussion about the connection which will serve as an additional knowledge.
After the discussion, the user can vary the transformer's rating and polarity.
Beside the main screen which is the trainer are the procedures for each connection in the practice part. Also, there are connecting wires that you need to click in order to start connecting. Clamp meter, digital ammeter and voltmeter are also provided in the trainer to get the values of line current, line voltage, phase current, phase voltage, apparent power and real power.
After performing the six connections, there will be an exercise to evaluate the user's learnings. The user's score will be shown after answering all of the questions.
